The ‘CalmClam’ aims to bridge this gap by gamifying emotional intelligence through the Inside Out  lens. It will help users :
     Identify which emotion is currently controlling/ driving the console.
     De-escalate the high intensity emotions like anxiety or anger using the empathetic thinking of the Calmclam to avoid hasty decisions.
     Reframe stressful situations into lessons where we study how to control our emotions, boosting our emotional intelligence, thereby helping us to restore balance to our internal headquarters (mind).
